N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 21.7 - Producer

State Regulations

Producer means any person, including members of any
cooperative association, who delivers milk of his own production to a pool
plant or whose milk is diverted by a marketer to a designated diversion plant
pursuant to section
21.17
